    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been meticulously addressed, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure peak chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the surgical turn-in and neutral handling balance the E46 is renowned for. The exterior finish exhibits zero clear coat failure, while the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feel. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a pristine, high-revving icon with full service documentation.",
