    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a breathtaking 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman, a vehicle that can only be described as a true time capsule. Finished in a deep Jet Black Metallic, the exterior has been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and a premium ceramic coating, resulting in a mirror-like finish completely free of swirls, rock chips, or scratches. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the Black leather interior retains its original factory scent, with no visible wear on the seat bolsters or steering wheel. Every electronic component and switch functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this Porsche is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. Recent maintenance includes a full fluid flush and a multi-point inspection. The sale includes the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and a binder of all service records. For the discerning buyer seeking a showroom-quality specimen, this vehicle stands as a testament to meticulous ownership.",
      "price": 46500.0,
